This paper is about biomedical event detection using a computational model based on a bi-directional LSTM network. The paper focuses on the context embedding of recognized arguments to capture the relations between them. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
